column5: Can any one provide info on the area of Dauphin River, Mantagao River on west side of Lake Winnipeg? I had some great northern and walleye fishing there in mid-May for several years in the 70's. Are there decent facilities there and could I still expect to find good fishing? Any contacts you would recommend?Thanks for any response
:( So did I. Those days have come and gone time to move on and look for a new fishing hole.
